      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance processes must meet MRL 5 requirements including version control, regression testing, and documented release procedures.",
      "rationale": "Version control and unit testing are in place; however, formal regression test suite coverage is incomplete and release documentation does not fully satisfy MRL 5 requirements."
