      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation must directly correspond to the clinical and regulatory quantities relevant to VAD hemolysis assessment.",
      "rationale": "Normalized index of hemolysis used as primary QoI aligns with ASTM F1841 standard; platelet activation index not assessed, representing a gap relative to full regulatory relevance."
