      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted under conditions sufficiently representative of the intended VAD operating envelope to support extrapolation to clinical use.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry under limited operating conditions; patient-specific geometry and pulsatile flow conditions not represented in validation dataset."
