      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence criteria and floating-point error bounds must be documented and demonstrated to be negligible relative to discretization error.",
      "rationale": "Iterative residual convergence documented; round-off and floating-point error analysis not performed. Factor flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
