      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Potential for user-introduced error in model setup, boundary condition specification, and post-processing must be systematically evaluated and mitigated.",
      "rationale": "No formal use error analysis conducted. Sensitivity of hemolysis predictions to user mesh setup choices not characterized. Flagged as epistemic gap."
    },
