      "acceptanceCriteria": "Justification for selection of turbulence model, hemolysis damage accumulation model, and constitutive relations must be provided with supporting evidence.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without systematic comparison to alternatives. Power-law hemolysis model adopted from literature without re-calibration. Model form uncertainty not quantified."
