      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sufficient experimental replicates must be available to characterize experimental variability and support statistically meaningful model-experiment comparison.",
      "rationale": "Single experimental dataset from FDA benchmark used; no independent replication across laboratories or blood sample donors. Sample size insufficient for MRL 5 statistical comparison."
    },
