      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Correspondence between experimental input parameters and simulation boundary conditions must be demonstrated quantitatively.",
      "rationale": "Nominal boundary conditions mapped from experimental protocol; uncertainty in actual experimental inlet conditions not reflected in simulation inputs. Equivalency not formally demonstrated."
